lley Coyote</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.hotyellow98.com/mystwalker/tao.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>w4nn4b3!</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>11/12/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>12:45:26 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.blizzard.com/images/broodwar/popup/lurker.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Solo class???</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">What is everyone opinion on wizards being a good solo class? Can we solo at lower levs? (lev. 1<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  If so whare can we solo at around lev 18 and up. <br>
