PS.  I don't even have bloody Jboots and can still kite.....(gotta admit it is nicer with sow)</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#D5D4D5><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uwilleycoyote.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Willey Coyote</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.hotyellow98.com/mystwalker/tao.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>l33t d00d!</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>12/7/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#000033>11:59:20 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.blizzard.com/images/broodwar/popup/lurker.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Solo class??? heck yeah they can</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Well my grouping skills have really improved. I had a chance to watch some experienced wizards in my group work and I learned lots from them. Now I feel that I can add alot to a group and not just drain mana from the healers because I get agroed on all the time. <br>
